# Approach
Alright, in this I am using Priority Queue. In this first I am adding all elements of the vector "stones" in the priority queue called "pq". Now I am initializing a while loop, setting the condition that, the size of "pq" must be greater than 1. I am simply checking the top 2 elements and doing the required manipulations in the question. In the end, if size of "pq" is 0, return 0; else we should return the top element of the same.

