Key point is servers are busy at times and idle at times .
Servers state is dynamic change with time .
At each sec we need server who is idle with least weight.
So these leads to idea for priority_queue which can give us least weight server at any time.
```
priority_queue: This can give us least weight server after any insertions and deletions .
```

Now, main idea:
1. we need two priority_queues for to maintain servers which are idle.
2. other one for servers which are processing the tasks.
pq1 = is straightforword , min heap with server weight as priority element
pq2 ==  ???
in pq2 = we can store processing time .
currentTime + tasks[j].

then its simple : just play with pq1 and pq2 .

use above argument as a hint and try it once .



